title: Independent candidate Tariq Mehmood Aryani wins PK-59 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Tariq Mehmood Aryani has won the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly election from PK-59, Mardan-VI by securing 28,349 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was ANP candidate Muhammad Haroon Khan who bagged 14,256 votes.
Voters turn-out remained 42.07 per cent.
